metadata.name: On the edge
metadata.description:
"On the Edge" is a work of art that captures the essence of relaxation and contemplation. The vibrant colors of pink, yellow, blue, and green dominate the scene, creating a feeling of warmth and serenity, inviting the viewer to step into the scene and experience the beauty of the moment for themselves.  
Digital Hand drawing  
JPG - 300 DPI  
2023
